premise_source_doc_sentence: In 1973 , Pisces V took part in the rescue of Roger Mallinson and Roger Chapman , who were trapped on the seabed in Pisces Vs sister submersible Pisces III .

In August 2002 , Pisces V and her sister Pisces IV discovered a World War II Japanese midget submarine outside of Pearl Harbor which had been sunk by the destroyer in the first American shots fired in World War II .
